replies.body:
Hi Meddler :)
Wukong news plz?
or candidate for small buff?? any time soon?  {{champion:62}}

Such an exciting time. I know a lot of people thought LoL would be dead by now, but clearly it's still going strong. There are a lot of people who don't like the current direction that Riot is taking, and have been taking for a while, and I feel the same way, however it's still exciting to be around for the 10th anniversary of the game, and I honestly hope that things can change for the better going forward.

I hope everyone, whether they're a Rioter or not, has an amazing day today!

{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
